7 An Act relating to the University Hospitals
Authority; making an appropriation; stating purpose;
8 providing an effective date; and declaring an
emergency.
9
10
11 BE IT ENACTED BY THE PEOPLE OF THE STATE OF OKLAHOMA:
12 SECTION 1. There is hereby appropriated to the University
13 Hospitals Authority, from any monies not otherwise appropriated from
14 the Statewide Recovery Fund (497) of the State Treasury, the sum of
15 Fifty Million Dollars ($50,000,000.00) or so much thereof as may be
16 necessary to address gaps in funding for the adolescent behavioral
17 health center. Such funds shall be utilized in a manner consistent
18 with the recommendations adopted by the Joint Committee on Pandemic
19 Relief Funding on April 15, 2026.
20 SECTION 2. This act shall become effective July 1, 2026.
21 SECTION 3. It being immediately necessary for the preservation
22 of the public peace, health or safety, an emergency is hereby
23 declared to exist, by reason whereof this act shall take effect and
24 be in full force from and after its passage and approval.
